{"type":"message","id":"9fa58b4b","parentId":"5a3bbe0e","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:23.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我作为子代理完成安全权限和审计系统的开发任务。让我先查看现有的项目结构和参考文档，然后快速开始实现。\n\n我需要：\n1. 先查看现有的Tianyou.Auth模块\n2. 查看云苍穹的安全开发文档\n3. 快速构建完整的权限和审计系统\n\n时间紧迫，让我立即开始。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"我立即开始执行刑部紧急任务。首先快速了解现有项目结构和参考文档。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8ee67b8ea47841618c12919c","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/knowledge-base/金蝶云苍穹/二开文档/07-安全开发.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_bb91e14e7e7a4fe190061e0d","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/src/Tianyou.Auth -type f -name \"*.cs\" 2>/dev/null | head -20"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8192866711a0487fb7db4c02","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/src/Tianyou.Auth/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":5406,"output":208,"cacheRead":10752,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16366,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774227314421}}
{"type":"message","id":"6e826f1d","parentId":"9fa58b4b","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:23.921Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8ee67b8ea47841618c12919c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 金蝶云苍穹安全开发文档\n\n**版本**: 金蝶云苍穹 v8.x  \n**文档ID**: JJC-20260320-001  \n**创建时间**: 2026-03-20\n\n---\n\n## 📋 概述\n\n金蝶云苍穹提供完善的安全体系，支持身份认证、权限控制、数据加密、安全审计等多个安全维度的保护。\n\n## 🔐 认证授权\n\n### 1. 认证方式\n\n**认证方式配置（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"authentication\": {\n    \"methods\": [\n      {\n        \"methodId\": \"password\",\n        \"methodName\": \"用户名密码认证\",\n        \"description\": \"最基础的认证方式\",\n        \"useCases\": [\n          \"Web应用登录\",\n          \"API调用认证\",\n          \"移动应用认证\"\n        ],\n        \"characteristics\": {\n          \"complexity\": \"low\",\n          \"security\": \"medium\",\n          \"userExperience\": \"basic\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"methodId\": \"sso\",\n        \"methodName\": \"单点登录\",\n        \"description\": \"支持多种SSO协议\",\n        \"useCases\": [\n          \"企业统一身份\",\n          \"跨系统登录\",\n          \"第三方集成\"\n        ],\n        \"supportedProtocols\": [\n          \"SAML 2.0\",\n          \"OAuth 2.0\",\n          \"OpenID Connect\",\n          \"CAS\"\n        ],\n        \"characteristics\": {\n          \"complexity\": \"high\",\n          \"security\": \"high\",\n          \"userExperience\": \"excellent\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"methodId\": \"mfa\",\n        \"methodName\": \"多因素认证\",\n        \"description\": \"提供额外的安全层\",\n        \"useCases\": [\n          \"敏感操作保护\",\n          \"管理员登录\",\n          \"异地登录\"\n        ],\n        \"factors\": [\n          {\n            \"factorId\": \"sms\",\n            \"factorName\": \"短信验证码\",\n            \"codeLength\": 6,\n            \"expiry\": 300\n          },\n          {\n            \"factorId\": \"email\",\n            \"factorName\": \"邮件验证码\",\n            \"codeLength\": 8,\n            \"expiry\": 600\n          },\n          {\n            \"factorId\": \"totp\",\n            \"factorName\": \"时间同步令牌\",\n            \"algorithm\": \"SHA-1\",\n            \"codeLength\": 6,\n            \"expiry\": 30\n          },\n          {\n            \"factorId\": \"biometric\",\n            \"factorName\": \"生物识别\",\n            \"supportedTypes\": [\n              \"fingerprint\",\n              \"face\",\n              \"iris\"\n            ]\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**C# 认证服务**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.Security.Authentication;\nusing K3Cloud.Security.Authorization;\n\npublic class AuthService\n{\n    private readonly IUserRepository _userRepository;\n    private readonly IPasswordHasher _passwordHasher;\n    private readonly IJwtTokenService _jwtTokenService;\n    private readonly IMfaService _mfaService;\n    private readonly IEventLogService _eventLog;\n    \n    public AuthService(\n        IUserRepository userRepository,\n        IPasswordHasher passwordHasher,\n        IJwtTokenService jwtTokenService,\n        IMfaService mfaService,\n        IEventLogService eventLog)\n    {\n        _userRepository = userRepository;\n        _passwordHasher = passwordHasher;\n        _jwtTokenService = jwtTokenService;\n        _mfaService = mfaService;\n        _eventLog = eventLog;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<LoginResult> LoginAsync(LoginRequest request)\n    {\n        // 1. 验证用户名和密码\n        var user = await _userRepository.GetByUsernameAsync(request.Username);\n        if (user == null || !user.IsActive)\n        {\n            await _eventLog.LogLoginFailureAsync(request.Username, \"用户不存在或已禁用\");\n            throw new AuthenticationException(\"用户名或密码错误\");\n        }\n        \n        var passwordValid = await _passwordHasher.VerifyAsync(\n            request.Password, \n            user.PasswordHash, \n            user.PasswordSalt\n        );\n        \n        if (!passwordValid)\n        {\n            await _eventLog.LogLoginFailureAsync(request.Username, \"密码错误\");\n            throw new AuthenticationException(\"用户名或密码错误\");\n        }\n        \n        // 2. 检查是否需要MFA\n        var mfaRequired = await CheckMfaRequiredAsync(user);\n        if (mfaRequired)\n        {\n            var mfaToken = await _mfaService.GenerateMfaTokenAsync(user.Id);\n            \n            return new LoginResult\n            {\n                Success = false,\n                RequireMfa = true,\n                MfaToken = mfaToken,\n                AvailableFactors = await _mfaService.GetAvailableFactorsAsync(user.Id)\n            };\n        }\n        \n        // 3. 生成访问令牌\n        var accessToken = await _jwtTokenService.GenerateTokenAsync(user);\n        var refreshToken = await _jwtTokenService.GenerateRefreshTokenAsync(user);\n        \n        // 4. 记录登录成功事件\n        await _eventLog.LogLoginSuccessAsync(user.Id, request.IpAddress, request.UserAgent);\n        \n        return new LoginResult\n        {\n            Success = true,\n            AccessToken = accessToken,\n            RefreshToken = refreshToken,\n            ExpiresIn = 3600,\n            User = new UserInfo\n            {\n                UserId = user.Id,\n                Username = user.Username,\n                Roles = user.Roles,\n                Permissions = user.Permissions\n            }\n        };\n    }\n    \n    private async Task<bool> CheckMfaRequiredAsync(User user)\n    {\n        // 管理员必须MFA\n        if (user.Roles.Contains(\"admin\"))\n        {\n            return true;\n        }\n        \n        // 异地登录需要MFA\n        var lastLogin = await _eventLog.GetLastLoginAsync(user.Id);\n        if (lastLogin != null && Is异地登录(lastLogin.IpAddress))\n        {\n            return true;\n        }\n        \n        // 敏感操作需要MFA\n        var hasSensitivePermissions = user.Permissions.Any(p => \n            p.StartsWith(\"sensitive\"));\n        \n        return hasSensitivePermissions;\n    }\n    \n    private bool Is异地登录(string lastIp, string currentIp)\n    {\n        // 简单的异地检测逻辑\n        return lastIp != currentIp && !IsLocalIp(currentIp);\n    }\n    \n    private bool IsLocalIp(string ip)\n    {\n        // 判断是否为本地IP\n        return ip.StartsWith(\"192.168.\") ||\n               ip.StartsWith(\"10.\") ||\n               ip == \"127.0.0.1\" ||\n               ip == \"::1\";\n    }\n}\n\npublic class LoginRequest\n{\n    public string Username { get; set; }\n    public string Password { get; set; }\n    public string IpAddress { get; set; }\n    public string UserAgent { get; set; }\n    public string MfaCode { get; set; } // MFA验证码\n    public string MfaToken { get; set; } // MFA令牌\n}\n\npublic class LoginResult\n{\n    public bool Success { get; set; }\n    public bool RequireMfa { get; set; }\n    public string MfaToken { get; set; }\n    public string AccessToken { get; set; }\n    public string RefreshToken { get; set; }\n    public int ExpiresIn { get; set; }\n    public UserInfo User { get; set; }\n    public List<MfaFactor> AvailableFactors { get; set; }\n}\n\npublic class MfaFactor\n{\n    public string FactorId { get; set; }\n    public string FactorName { get; set; }\n    public bool IsDefault { get; set; }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. 令牌管理\n\n**JWT令牌配置（C#）**:\n```csharp\nusing System.IdentityModel.Tokens.Jwt;\nusing Microsoft.IdentityModel.Tokens;\n\npublic class JwtTokenService : IJwtTokenService\n{\n    private readonly JwtSecurityTokenHandler _tokenHandler;\n    private readonly SigningCredentials _credentials;\n    private readonly JwtOptions _options;\n    \n    public JwtTokenService(IOptions<JwtOptions> options)\n    {\n        _options = options.Value;\n        \n        var key = Encoding.ASCII.GetBytes(_options.Secret);\n        _credentials = new SigningCredentials(\n            new SymmetricSecurityKey(key),\n            SecurityAlgorithms.HmacSha256\n        );\n        \n        _tokenHandler = new JwtSecurityTokenHandler(_credentials);\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<string> GenerateTokenAsync(User user)\n    {\n        var claims = new List<Claim>\n        {\n            new Claim(ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier, user.Id),\n            new Claim(ClaimTypes.Name, user.Username),\n            new Claim(JwtRegisteredClaimNames.Jti, Guid.NewGuid().ToString()),\n            new Claim(JwtRegisteredClaimNames.Iat, DateTimeOffset.UtcNow.ToUnixTimeSeconds().ToString())\n        };\n        \n        // 添加角色声明\n        foreach (var role in user.Roles)\n        {\n            claims.Add(new Claim(\"role\", role));\n        }\n        \n        // 添加权限声明\n        foreach (var permission in user.Permissions)\n        {\n            claims.Add(new Claim(\"permission\", permission));\n        }\n        \n        var tokenDescriptor = new SecurityTokenDescriptor\n        {\n            Subject = user.Id,\n            Expires = DateTime.UtcNow.AddHours(_options.ExpirationHours),\n            Issuer = _options.Issuer,\n            Audience = _options.Audience,\n            Claims = claims\n        };\n        \n        var token = _tokenHandler.CreateToken(tokenDescriptor);\n        return token;\n    }\n    \n    public ClaimsPrincipal ValidateToken(string token)\n    {\n        var tokenHandler = new JwtSecurityTokenHandler(_credentials);\n        \n        try\n        {\n            var principal = tokenHandler.ValidateToken(token, \n                    new TokenValidationParameters\n                    {\n                        ValidateIssuer = true,\n                        ValidIssuer = _options.Issuer,\n                        ValidateAudience = true,\n                        ValidAudience = _options.Audience,\n                        ValidateLifetime = true,\n                        Clock = DateTime.UtcNow\n                    }, \n                    out var validatedToken);\n            \n            return principal;\n        }\n        catch (SecurityTokenExpiredException)\n        {\n            throw new SecurityTokenException(\"访问令牌已过期\");\n        }\n        catch (SecurityTokenInvalidSignatureException)\n        {\n            throw new SecurityTokenException(\"访问令牌签名无效\");\n        }\n    }\n}\n\npublic class JwtOptions\n{\n    public string Secret { get; set; }\n    public string Issuer { get; set; }\n    public string Audience { get; set; }\n    public int ExpirationHours { get; set; } = 24\n}\n```\n\n## 🔒 权限控制\n\n### 1. RBAC权限模型\n\n**权限模型定义（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"rbac\": {\n    \"roles\": [\n      {\n        \"roleId\": \"admin\",\n        \"roleName\": \"系统管理员\",\n        \"description\": \"拥有所有权限\",\n        \"isSystem\": true,\n        \"permissions\": [\"*\"]\n      },\n      {\n        \"roleId\": \"dept_manager\",\n        \"roleName\": \"部门经理\",\n        \"description\": \"管理本部门和下属\",\n        \"permissions\": [\n          \"bill:create\",\n          \"bill:read\",\n          \"bill:update\",\n          \"bill:delete\",\n          \"bill:approve\",\n          \"user:read\",\n          \"report:view\"\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"roleId\": \"sales_staff\",\n        \"roleName\": \"销售人员\",\n        \"description\": \"销售人员权限\",\n        \"permissions\": [\n          \"bill:create\",\n          \"bill:read\",\n          \"customer:read\",\n          \"product:read\"\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"roleId\": \"viewer\",\n        \"roleName\": \"查看者\",\n        \"description\": \"只读权限\",\n        \"permissions\": [\n          \"bill:read\",\n          \"report:view\"\n        ]\n      }\n    ],\n    \"resources\": [\n      {\n        \"resourceId\": \"bill\",\n        \"resourceName\": \"单据\",\n        \"actions\": [\"create\", \"read\", \"update\", \"delete\", \"approve\", \"export\"]\n      },\n      {\n        \"resourceId\": \"user\",\n        \"resourceName\": \"用户\",\n        \"actions\": [\"create\", \"read\", \"update\", \"delete\", \"assign_role\"]\n      },\n      {\n        \"resourceId\": \"report\",\n        \"resourceName\": \"报表\",\n        \"actions\": [\"view\", \"export\", \"schedule\"]\n      },\n      {\n        \"resourceId\": \"system\",\n        \"resourceName\": \"系统\",\n        \"actions\": [\"config\", \"monitor\", \"audit\"]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**C# 权限服务**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.Security.Authorization;\n\npublic class PermissionService : IPermissionService\n{\n    private readonly IPermissionRepository _repository;\n    private readonly IRoleRepository _roleRepository;\n    \n    public PermissionService(\n        IPermissionRepository repository,\n        IRoleRepository roleRepository)\n    {\n        _repository = repository;\n        _roleRepository = roleRepository;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<bool> HasPermissionAsync(string userId, string resource, string action)\n    {\n        // 获取用户角色\n        var userRoles = await _repository.GetUserRolesAsync(userId);\n        \n        foreach (var roleId in userRoles)\n        {\n            var role = await _roleRepository.GetByIdAsync(roleId);\n            \n            // 检查是否是管理员\n            if (role.IsSystem && role.Permissions.Contains(\"*\"))\n            {\n                return true;\n            }\n            \n            // 检查是否有权限\n            var hasPermission = role.Permissions.Contains($\"{resource}:{action}\");\n            if (hasPermission)\n            {\n                return true;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return false;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<bool> HasAnyPermissionAsync(string userId, List<string> permissions)\n    {\n        var userRoles = await _repository.GetUserRolesAsync(userId);\n        \n        foreach (var roleId in userRoles)\n        {\n            var role = await _roleRepository.GetByIdAsync(roleId);\n            \n            if (role.IsSystem && role.Permissions.Contains(\"*\"))\n            {\n                return true;\n            }\n            \n            var hasAny = role.Permissions.Any(p => permissions.Contains(p));\n            if (hasAny)\n            {\n                return true;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        return false;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<AuthorizationResult> CheckAuthorizationAsync(\n        string userId, \n        string resource, \n        string action)\n    {\n        var hasPermission = await HasPermissionAsync(userId, resource, action);\n        \n        if (!hasPermission)\n        {\n            return new AuthorizationResult\n            {\n                Allowed = false,\n                Reason = \"权限不足\",\n                RequiredPermission = $\"{resource}:{action}\"\n            };\n        }\n        \n        return new AuthorizationResult { Allowed = true };\n    }\n}\n\npublic class AuthorizationResult\n{\n    public bool Allowed { get; set; }\n    public string Reason { get; set; }\n    public string RequiredPermission { get; set; }\n}\n```\n\n### 2. 数据权限\n\n**数据权限定义（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"dataPermissions\": {\n    \"types\": [\n      {\n        \"typeId\": \"row_level\",\n        \"typeName\": \"行级权限\",\n        \"description\": \"控制用户只能看到特定的行\",\n        \"fields\": [\"creator\", \"dept\", \"region\", \"organization\"],\n        \"rules\": [\n          {\n            \"ruleId\": \"own_data\",\n            \"ruleName\": \"只能看自己的数据\",\n            \"condition\": \"creator == current_user\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"ruleId\": \"dept_data\",\n            \"ruleName\": \"只能看本部门数据\",\n            \"condition\": \"dept == current_user_dept\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"ruleId\": \"org_data\",\n            \"ruleName\": \"只能看本组织数据\",\n            \"condition\": \"organization == current_user_org\"\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"typeId\": \"column_level\",\n        \"typeName\": \"列级权限\",\n        \"description\": \"控制用户只能看到特定的列\",\n        \"fields\": [\"amount\", \"profit\", \"salary\", \"commission\"],\n        \"implementation\": \"动态SQL查询\"\n      },\n      {\n        \"typeId\": \"filter_level\",\n        \"typeName\": \"过滤权限\",\n        \"description\": \"自动过滤数据查询\",\n        \"implementation\": \"WHERE子句注入\"\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**C# 数据权限过滤器**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.Security.Data;\n\npublic class DataPermissionFilter\n{\n    private readonly ICurrentUserService _currentUser;\n    \n    public DataPermissionFilter(ICurrentUserService currentUser)\n    {\n        _currentUser = currentUser;\n    }\n    \n    public IQueryable<T> ApplyDataPermissions<T>(\n        IQueryable<T> query, \n        string resourceType) where T : class\n    {\n        var user = _currentUser.GetCurrentUser();\n        var dataPermissions = user.GetDataPermissions(resourceType);\n        \n        if (!dataPermissions.Any())\n        {\n            return query;\n        }\n        \n        // 应用行级权限\n        foreach (var permission in dataPermissions.Where(p => p.Type == \"row_level\"))\n        {\n            query = ApplyRowLevelPermission(query, permission);\n        }\n        \n        // 应用列级权限\n        var columnsToHide = dataPermissions\n            .Where(p => p.Type == \"column_level\")\n            .Select(p => p.Field)\n            .ToList();\n        \n        query = ApplyColumnLevelPermissions(query, columnsToHide);\n        \n        return query;\n    }\n    \n    private IQueryable<T> ApplyRowLevelPermission<T>(\n        IQueryable<T> query, \n        DataPermission permission) where T : class\n    {\n        // 使用动态表达式构建过滤器\n        var parameter = Expression.Parameter(typeof(T));\n        var property = Expression.Property(parameter, permission.Field);\n        \n        var value = _currentUser.GetPropertyValue(permission.Field);\n        var comparison = Expression.Equal(property, Expression.Constant(value));\n        \n        var lambda = Expression.Lambda(comparison, parameter);\n        return query.Where(lambda);\n    }\n    \n    private IQueryable<T> ApplyColumnLevelPermissions<T>(\n        IQueryable<T> query, \n        List<string> columnsToHide) where T : class\n    {\n        if (!columnsToHide.Any())\n        {\n            return query;\n        }\n        \n        // 使用Select隐藏指定列\n        var parameter = Expression.Parameter(typeof(T));\n        var bindings = new List<MemberBinding>();\n        \n        // 获取所有属性\n        var properties = typeof(T).GetProperties(BindingFlags.Public | BindingFlags.Instance)\n            .Where(p => !columnsToHide.Contains(p.Name))\n            .ToList();\n        \n        foreach (var property in properties)\n        {\n            var member = Expression.Property(parameter, property.Name);\n            bindings.Add(member);\n        }\n        \n        var selector = Expression.Lambda(Expression.New(typeof(T), bindings.ToArray()), parameter);\n        return query.Select(selector);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 🔐 数据加密\n\n### 1. 加密算法\n\n**加密算法配置（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"encryption\": {\n    \"algorithms\": [\n      {\n        \"algorithmId\": \"aes_256\",\n        \"algorithmName\": \"AES-256\",\n        \"description\": \"对称加密，数据传输和存储\",\n        \"keySize\": 256,\n        \"blockSize\": 128,\n        \"modes\": [\"ECB\", \"CBC\", \"CTR\"],\n        \"useCases\": [\n          \"数据库字段加密\",\n          \"API数据加密\",\n          \"文件存储加密\"\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"algorithmId\": \"rsa_2048\",\n        \"algorithmName\": \"RSA-2048\",\n        \"description\": \"非对称加密，密钥交换\",\n        \"keySize\": 2048,\n        \"useCases\": [\n          \"敏感数据传输\",\n          \"数字签名\",\n          \"密钥协商\"\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"algorithmId\": \"sha_256\",\n        \"algorithmName\": \"SHA-256\",\n        \"description\": \"哈希算法，数据完整性\",\n        \"outputSize\": 256,\n        \"useCases\": [\n          \"密码哈希\",\n          \"文件校验\",\n          \"数字签名\"\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**C# 加密服务**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.Security.Encryption;\nusing System.Security.Cryptography;\n\npublic class EncryptionService : IEncryptionService\n{\n    private readonly IConfiguration _config;\n    \n    public EncryptionService(IConfiguration config)\n    {\n        _config = config;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<string> EncryptAsync(string plainText)\n    {\n        var algorithm = _config[\"Encryption:DefaultAlgorithm\"] ?? \"AES-256-CBC\";\n        \n        switch (algorithm)\n        {\n            case \"AES-256-CBC\":\n                return await EncryptAes256CbcAsync(plainText);\n            case \"AES-256-CTR\":\n                return await EncryptAes256CtrAsync(plainText);\n            default:\n                throw new NotSupportedException($\"不支持的加密算法: {algorithm}\");\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private async Task<string> EncryptAes256CbcAsync(string plainText)\n    {\n        var key = GetEncryptionKey();\n        var iv = GenerateIv();\n        \n        using var aes = Aes.Create();\n        aes.Key = key;\n        aes.IV = iv;\n        aes.Mode = CipherMode.CBC;\n        aes.Padding = PaddingMode.PKCS7;\n        \n        var encryptor = aes.CreateEncryptor();\n        using var msEncrypt = new MemoryStream();\n        {\n            using (var csEncrypt = new CryptoStream(msEncrypt, encryptor, CryptoStreamMode.Write))\n            {\n                using (var swEncrypt = new StreamWriter(csEncrypt))\n                {\n                    swEncrypt.Write(plainText);\n                }\n            }\n            \n            return Convert.ToBase64String(msEncrypt.ToArray());\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private async Task<string> EncryptAes256CtrAsync(string plainText)\n    {\n        var key = GetEncryptionKey();\n        \n        using var aes = Aes.Create();\n        aes.Key = key;\n        aes.Mode = CipherMode.CTR;\n        aes.Padding = PaddingMode.PKCS7;\n        \n        var encryptor = aes.CreateEncryptor();\n        using var msEncrypt = new MemoryStream();\n        {\n            using (var csEncrypt = new CryptoStream(msEncrypt, encryptor, CryptoStreamMode.Write))\n            {\n                using (var swEncrypt = new StreamWriter(csEncrypt))\n                {\n                    swEncrypt.Write(plainText);\n                }\n            }\n            \n            var cipherText = new byte[msEncrypt.Length + 16]; // AES-CTR需要16字节的nonce\n            Buffer.BlockCopy(msEncrypt.ToArray(), 0, cipherText, msEncrypt.Length);\n            Buffer.BlockCopy(msEncrypt.ToArray(), 0, cipherText, msEncrypt.Length, 16, 16);\n            \n            return Convert.ToBase64String(cipherText);\n        }\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<string> DecryptAsync(string cipherText)\n    {\n        var iv = GetIvFromCipherText(cipherText);\n        var key = GetEncryptionKey();\n        \n        using var aes = Aes.Create();\n        aes.Key = key;\n        aes.IV = iv;\n        \n        var decryptor = aes.CreateDecryptor();\n        var cipherBytes = Convert.FromBase64String(cipherText);\n        \n        using var msDecrypt = new MemoryStream(cipherBytes);\n        using (var csDecrypt = new CryptoStream(msDecrypt, decryptor, CryptoStreamMode.Read))\n        {\n            using (var srDecrypt = new StreamReader(csDecrypt))\n            {\n                return await srDecrypt.ReadToEndAsync();\n            }\n        }\n    }\n    \n    private byte[] GetEncryptionKey()\n    {\n        var key = _config[\"Encryption:Key\"];\n        return Convert.FromBase64String(key);\n    }\n    \n    private byte[] GenerateIv()\n    {\n        var iv = new byte[16];\n        using (var rng = RandomNumberGenerator.Create())\n        {\n            rng.GetBytes(iv);\n        }\n        return iv;\n    }\n    \n    private byte[] GetIvFromCipherText(string cipherText)\n    {\n        var bytes = Convert.FromBase64String(cipherText);\n        var iv = new byte[16];\n        Buffer.BlockCopy(bytes, bytes.Length - 16, iv, 0, 16);\n        return iv;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 📊 安全审计\n\n### 1. 审计日志\n\n**审计日志配置（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"audit\": {\n    \"events\": [\n      {\n        \"eventId\": \"user_login\",\n        \"eventName\": \"用户登录\",\n        \"level\": \"info\",\n        \"categories\": [\"authentication\"],\n        \"include\": [\"ip_address\", \"user_agent\", \"login_time\"]\n      },\n      {\n        \"eventId\": \"user_logout\",\n        \"eventName\": \"用户退出\",\n        \"level\": \"info\",\n        \"categories\": [\"authentication\"],\n        \"include\": [\"logout_time\"]\n      },\n      {\n        \"eventId\": \"permission_denied\",\n        \"eventName\": \"权限拒绝\",\n        \"level\": \"warning\",\n        \"categories\": [\"authorization\"],\n        \"include\": [\"user\", \"resource\", \"action\", \"ip_address\"]\n      },\n      {\n        \"eventId\": \"sensitive_data_access\",\n        \"eventName\": \"敏感数据访问\",\n        \"level\": \"high\",\n        \"categories\": [\"data_protection\"],\n        \"include\": [\"user\", \"resource\", \"action\", \"data_fields\"]\n      },\n      {\n        \"eventId\": \"system_config_change\",\n        \"eventName\": \"系统配置变更\",\n        \"level\": \"warning\",\n        \"categories\": [\"system\"],\n        \"include\": [\"operator\", \"config_key\", \"old_value\", \"new_value\"]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**C# 审计服务**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.Security.Audit;\n\npublic class AuditService : IAuditService\n{\n    private readonly IAuditLogRepository _repository;\n    private readonly ICurrentUser _currentUser;\n    \n    public AuditService(IAuditLogRepository repository, ICurrentUser currentUser)\n    {\n        _repository = repository;\n        _currentUser = currentUser;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task LogAsync(AuditEvent auditEvent)\n    {\n        var log = new AuditLog\n        {\n            EventId = auditEvent.EventId,\n            EventName = auditEvent.EventName,\n            Level = auditEvent.Level,\n            Categories = auditEvent.Categories,\n            Timestamp = DateTime.UtcNow,\n            IpAddress = _currentUser.GetIpAddress(),\n            UserAgent = _currentUser.GetUserAgent(),\n            UserId = _currentUser.GetUserId()\n        };\n        \n        // 添加事件数据\n        if (auditEvent.Data != null)\n        {\n            foreach (var item in auditEvent.Data)\n            {\n                log.SetData(item.Key, item.Value);\n            }\n        }\n        \n        await _repository.AddAsync(log);\n    }\n    \n    public async Task LogLoginSuccessAsync(string userId, string ipAddress, string userAgent)\n    {\n        var auditEvent = new AuditEvent\n        {\n            EventId = \"user_login\",\n            EventName = \"用户登录成功\",\n            Level = \"info\",\n            Categories = new List<string> { \"authentication\" },\n            Data = new Dictionary<string, object>\n            {\n                { \"login_status\", \"success\" },\n                { \"login_time\", DateTime.UtcNow }\n            }\n        };\n        \n        await LogAsync(auditEvent);\n    }\n    \n    public async Task LogPermissionDeniedAsync(\n        string userId, \n        string resource, \n        string action,\n        string reason)\n    {\n        var auditEvent = new AuditEvent\n        {\n            EventId = \"permission_denied\",\n            EventName = \"权限拒绝\",\n            Level = \"warning\",\n            Categories = new List<string> { \"authorization\" },\n            Data = new Dictionary<string, object>\n            {\n                { \"resource\", resource },\n                { \"action\", action },\n                { \"reason\", reason }\n            }\n        };\n        \n        await LogAsync(auditEvent);\n    }\n    \n    public async Task<List<AuditLog>> QueryAsync(AuditQuery query)\n    {\n        return await _repository.QueryAsync(query);\n    }\n}\n\npublic class AuditEvent\n{\n    public string EventId { get; set; }\n    public string EventName { get; set; }\n    public string Level { get; set; }  // info, warning, error, critical\n    public List<string> Categories { get; set; }\n    public Dictionary<string, object> Data { get; set; }\n}\n```\n\n## 🛠️ 漏洞防护\n\n### 1. OWASP Top 10防护\n\n**防护配置（JSON）**:\n```json\n{\n  \"owasp\": {\n    \"protections\": [\n      {\n        \"owaspId\": \"injection\",\n        \"protectionName\": \"注入防护\",\n        \"description\": \"防止SQL注入、命令注入等\",\n        \"implementations\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"参数化查询\",\n            \"description\": \"使用参数化查询，避免字符串拼接\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"输入验证\",\n            \"description\": \"验证所有输入，过滤危险字符\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"ORM框架\",\n            \"description\": \"使用成熟的ORM框架，自动处理参数\"\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"owaspId\": \"broken_authentication\",\n        \"protectionName\": \"失效的身份认证\",\n        \"description\": \"防止会话劫持、固定会话ID\",\n        \"implementations\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"安全的会话管理\",\n            \"description\": \"使用随机生成的会话ID\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"会话超时\",\n            \"description\": \"设置合理的会话超时时间\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"HTTPS强制\",\n            \"description\": \"生产环境强制使用HTTPS\"\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"owaspId\": \"xss\",\n        \"protectionName\": \"跨站脚本攻击\",\n        \"description\": \"防止XSS攻击\",\n        \"implementations\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"输出编码\",\n            \"description\": \"对所有输出进行HTML编码\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"CSP策略\",\n            \"description\": \"设置内容安全策略\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"XSS防护库\",\n            \"description\": \"使用成熟的XSS防护库\"\n          }\n        ]\n      },\n      {\n        \"owaspId\": \"csrf\",\n        \"protectionName\": \"跨站请求伪造\",\n        \"description\": \"防止CSRF攻击\",\n        \"implementations\": [\n          {\n            \"name\": \"Anti-CSRF Token\",\n            \"description\": \"在表单中添加CSRF令牌\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"SameSite Cookie\",\n            \"description\": \"设置Cookie的SameSite属性\"\n          },\n          {\n            \"name\": \"Referer检查\",\n            \"description\": \"验证HTTP Referer头\"\n          }\n        ]\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**C# 中间件**:\n```csharp\nusing K3Cloud.Security.Middleware;\nusing Microsoft.AspNetCore.Http;\n\npublic class SecurityHeadersMiddleware\n{\n    private readonly RequestDelegate _next;\n    \n    public SecurityHeadersMiddleware(RequestDelegate next)\n    {\n        _next = next;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task InvokeAsync(HttpContext context)\n    {\n        // 添加安全响应头\n        context.Response.Headers.Add(\"X-Content-Type-Options\", \"nosniff\");\n        context.Response.Headers.Add(\"X-Frame-Options\", \"SAMEORIGIN\");\n        context.Response.Headers.Add(\"X-XSS-Protection\", \"1; mode=block\");\n        context.Response.Headers.Add(\"Content-Security-Policy\", \"default-src 'self'\");\n        \n        await _next(context);\n    }\n}\n\npublic class AntiCsrfMiddleware\n{\n    private readonly IAntiCsrfService _antiCsrf;\n    \n    public AntiCsrfMiddleware(IAntiCsrfService antiCsrf)\n    {\n        _antiCsrf = antiCsrf;\n    }\n    \n    public async Task InvokeAsync(HttpContext context)\n    {\n        // 验证POST/PUT/DELETE请求\n        if (HttpMethods.IsPost(context.Request.Method) ||\n            HttpMethods.IsPut(context.Request.Method) ||\n            HttpMethods.IsDelete(context.Request.Method))\n        {\n            var token = context.Request.Headers[\"X-CSRF-TOKEN\"];\n            \n            if (string.IsNullOrEmpty(token) || !_antiCsrf.ValidateToken(token))\n            {\n                context.Response.StatusCode = 403;\n                await context.Response.WriteAsync(\"CSRF token validation failed\");\n                return;\n            }\n        }\n        \n        await _next(context);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 📝 最佳实践\n\n### 1. 密码安全\n- 最小长度：8个字符\n- 复杂度：必须包含大小写字母、数字和特殊字符\n- 定期更换：每90天更换一次\n- 密码哈希：使用PBKDF2或Argon2\n\n### 2. 会话管理\n- 使用安全的会话ID\n- 设置合理的超时时间（30分钟）\n- 登出时立即销毁会话\n- 防止会话固定\n\n### 3. API安全\n- 使用HTTPS\n- 实施请求速率限制\n- 验证输入参数\n- 最小化数据暴露\n\n### 4. 代码安全\n- 避免硬编码密钥\n- 使用最新的依赖库\n- 定期进行安全审计\n- 遵循安全编码规范\n\n## 📚 相关资源\n\n- **安全文档**: https://developer.kingdee.com/security\n- **最佳实践**: https://developer.kingdee.com/security/best-practices\n- **OWASP指南**: https://owasp.org/www-project-top-ten\n\n---\n\n**文档版本**: v8.0  \n**最后更新**: 2026-03-20  \n**作者**: 太子\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227323921}}
