{"type":"message","id":"a042fc08","parentId":"2a5a5c79","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:28.841Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到：\n1. 项目已经有一个Tianyou.Auth模块，有一些基础结构\n2. 云苍穹的安全文档很详细，包含了JWT认证、RBAC权限、数据权限、加密、审计等\n\n现在我需要快速查看现有代码，然后补充完善所有功能。让我先看看现有的实现。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我看到项目已经有基础的Auth模块。让我快速查看现有实现，然后补充完善所有安全权限和审计功能。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b517b05f2ecb4aa1a58e7d7d","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/src/Tianyou.Auth/README.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_e539be0d1d76404c8b034ddd","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/src/Tianyou.Auth/Models/User.cs"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_23e9407007d241199247e6ee","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/src/Tianyou.Auth/Services/AuthService.cs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":8214,"output":193,"cacheRead":16128,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":24535,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774227323923}}
{"type":"message","id":"1b642822","parentId":"a042fc08","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:28.872Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b517b05f2ecb4aa1a58e7d7d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Tianyou.Auth - 认证授权模块\n\n完整的认证授权系统，支持JWT Bearer认证和RBAC权限模型。\n\n## 功能特性\n\n### 1. 认证模块 (Authentication)\n- JWT Bearer Token认证\n- 用户登录/登出\n- 用户注册\n- Token刷新机制\n- 密码修改和重置\n- 邮箱验证\n\n### 2. 权限模块 (Authorization)\n- 基于角色的访问控制 (RBAC)\n- 基于权限的细粒度控制\n- 权限策略定义\n- 权限验证处理器\n\n### 3. 数据访问控制\n- 数据过滤（按用户/组织/部门）\n- 字段级安全控制\n- 敏感数据自动过滤\n\n### 4. 安全工具\n- 密码哈希（PBKDF2）\n- 数据加密（AES-256）\n- 密码强度验证\n- 用户输入验证\n\n### 5. 审计日志\n- 用户操作记录\n- 数据变更追踪\n- 安全事件日志\n\n## 目录结构\n\n```\nsrc/Tianyou.Auth/\n├── Models/                    # 数据模型\n│   ├── User.cs               # 用户模型\n│   ├── Role.cs               # 角色模型\n│   ├── Permission.cs         # 权限模型\n│   └── TokenInfo.cs          # Token信息模型\n├── Services/                  # 服务层\n│   ├── IAuthService.cs       # 认证服务接口\n│   ├── AuthService.cs        # 认证服务实现\n│   └── TokenService.cs       # Token生成服务\n├── Authorization/             # 权限控制\n│   ├── PermissionHandler.cs  # 权限处理器\n│   ├── PermissionRequirement.cs # 权限需求\n│   └── RolePermission.cs     # 角色权限映射\n├── DataSecurity/              # 数据安全\n│   ├── DataFilter.cs         # 数据过滤器\n│   ├── FieldSecurity.cs      # 字段级安全\n│   └── AuditLog.cs           # 审计日志\n├── Security/                  # 安全工具\n│   ├── PasswordHasher.cs     # 密码哈希\n│   ├── EncryptionService.cs  # 加密服务\n│   └── SecurityValidator.cs  # 安全验证\n├── Controllers/               # API控制器\n│   ├── AuthController.cs     # 认证API\n│   ├── UserController.cs     # 用户管理API\n│   ├── RoleController.cs     # 角色管理API\n│   └── PermissionController.cs # 权限管理API\n├── ServiceCollectionExtensions.cs # 服务注册扩展\n└── Tianyou.Auth.csproj       # 项目文件\n```\n\n## 配置\n\n### appsettings.json 配置示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"Jwt\": {\n    \"SecretKey\": \"your-secret-key-at-least-32-characters-long\",\n    \"Issuer\": \"Tianyou\",\n    \"Audience\": \"Tianyou.Client\",\n    \"AccessTokenExpirationMinutes\": 60,\n    \"RefreshTokenExpirationDays\": 7\n  },\n  \"Security\": {\n    \"EncryptionKey\": \"your-encryption-key\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n## 使用方法\n\n### 1. 注册服务\n\n在 `Program.cs` 或 `Startup.cs` 中：\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Auth;\n\nvar builder = WebApplication.CreateBuilder(args);\n\n// 添加Tianyou认证授权服务\nbuilder.Services.AddTianyouAuth(builder.Configuration);\n\n// 添加控制器\nbuilder.Services.AddControllers();\n\nvar app = builder.Build();\n\n// 使用认证和授权中间件\napp.UseAuthentication();\napp.UseAuthorization();\n\napp.MapControllers();\napp.Run();\n```\n\n### 2. 使用认证API\n\n#### 用户登录\n```http\nPOST /api/auth/login\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"username\": \"admin\",\n  \"password\": \"P@ssw0rd123\"\n}\n```\n\n响应：\n```json\n{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"message\": \"登录成功\",\n  \"tokenInfo\": {\n    \"accessToken\": \"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIs...\",\n    \"refreshToken\": \"vGhI2hT3...\",\n    \"tokenType\": \"Bearer\",\n    \"expiresIn\": 3600,\n    \"expiresAt\": \"2026-03-22T23:00:00Z\",\n    \"userId\": \"123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000\",\n    \"username\": \"admin\",\n    \"roles\": [\"admin\"],\n    \"permissions\": [\"user:create\", \"user:read\", ...]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n#### 用户注册\n```http\nPOST /api/auth/register\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"username\": \"newuser\",\n  \"email\": \"user@example.com\",\n  \"password\": \"P@ssw0rd123\",\n  \"phoneNumber\": \"+8613800138000\"\n}\n```\n\n#### 刷新Token\n```http\nPOST /api/auth/refresh\nContent-Type: application/json\n\n{\n  \"refreshToken\": \"vGhI2hT3...\"\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 使用权限控制\n\n#### 在控制器方法上使用权限策略\n\n```csharp\n[ApiController]\n[Route(\"api/[controller]\")]\n[Authorize]\npublic class ProductController : ControllerBase\n{\n    [HttpGet]\n    [Authorize(Policy = \"UserRead\")]\n    public IActionResult GetProducts()\n    {\n        // 只有拥有 user:read 权限的用户才能访问\n        return Ok();\n    }\n\n    [HttpPost]\n    [Authorize(Policy = \"UserCreate\")]\n    public IActionResult CreateProduct([FromBody] Product product)\n    {\n        // 只有拥有 user:create 权限的用户才能访问\n        return Ok();\n    }\n\n    [HttpDelete(\"{id}\")]\n    [Authorize(Roles = \"admin\")]\n    public IActionResult DeleteProduct(Guid id)\n    {\n        // 只有admin角色才能访问\n        return Ok();\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 4. 数据过滤\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Auth.DataSecurity;\n\n// 过滤用户自己的数据\nvar userOrders = dbContext.Orders\n    .FilterByUser(User, o => o.UserId);\n\n// 过滤组织数据\nvar orgData = dbContext.Documents\n    .FilterByOrganization(User, d => d.OrganizationId);\n\n// 检查数据访问权限\nif (!DataFilter.HasDataAccess(User, document, d => d.OwnerId))\n{\n    return Forbid();\n}\n```\n\n### 5. 字段级安全\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Auth.DataSecurity;\n\n// 自动过滤敏感字段\nvar userRoles = User.FindAll(ClaimTypes.Role).Select(c => c.Value).ToList();\nvar safeUser = FieldSecurity.FilterSensitiveFields(user, userRoles);\n```\n\n### 6. 审计日志\n\n```csharp\nusing Tianyou.Auth.DataSecurity;\n\npublic class OrderController : ControllerBase\n{\n    private readonly AuditLogService _auditLogService;\n\n    [HttpPost]\n    public IActionResult CreateOrder([FromBody] Order order)\n    {\n        // ... 创建订单逻辑 ...\n\n        _auditLogService.Log(\n            User,\n            AuditAction.Create,\n            \"Order\",\n            order.Id.ToString(),\n            $\"创建订单 {order.OrderNumber}\",\n            null,\n            order);\n\n        return Ok(order);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n## 预定义角色和权限\n\n### 系统角色\n- **admin** - 超级管理员，拥有所有权限\n- **user_manager** - 用户管理员，管理用户和角色\n- **user** - 普通用户，拥有基本权限\n- **auditor** - 审计员，拥有只读权限\n\n### 权限常量\n```csharp\n// 用户权限\nPermissionConstants.UserCreate    // \"user:create\"\nPermissionConstants.UserRead      // \"user:read\"\nPermissionConstants.UserUpdate    // \"user:update\"\nPermissionConstants.UserDelete    // \"user:delete\"\n\n// 角色权限\nPermissionConstants.RoleCreate    // \"role:create\"\nPermissionConstants.RoleRead      // \"role:read\"\nPermissionConstants.RoleUpdate    // \"role:update\"\nPermissionConstants.RoleDelete    // \"role:delete\"\n\n// 权限管理\nPermissionConstants.PermissionCreate  // \"permission:create\"\nPermissionConstants.PermissionRead    // \"permission:read\"\nPermissionConstants.PermissionUpdate  // \"permission:update\"\nPermissionConstants.PermissionDelete  // \"permission:delete\"\n```\n\n## 安全建议\n\n1. **JWT密钥**：使用强密钥（至少32字符），定期更换\n2. **密码策略**：要求复杂密码（大小写+数字+特殊字符）\n3. **Token过期**：设置合理的过期时间（建议1小时）\n4. **HTTPS**：生产环境必须使用HTTPS\n5. **审计日志**：定期检查审计日志，监控异常行为\n6. **加密密钥**：妥善保管加密密钥，不要硬编码\n\n## 依赖项\n\n- .NET 8.0\n- Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authentication.JwtBearer\n- Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization\n- Microsoft.Extensions.Configuration\n- Microsoft.Extensions.DependencyInjection\n- Microsoft.Extensions.Logging\n\n## 许可证\n\nCopyright © 2026 Tianyou\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227328872}}
{"type":"message","id":"b602fb88","parentId":"1b642822","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:28.873Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_e539be0d1d76404c8b034ddd","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using System;\nusing System.Collections.Generic;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Auth.Models\n{\n    /// <summary>\n    /// 用户模型\n    /// </summary>\n    public class User\n    {\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 用户ID\n        /// </summary>\n        public Guid Id { get; set; }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 用户名\n        /// </summary>\n        public string Username { get; set; } = string.Empty;\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 电子邮件\n        /// </summary>\n        public string Email { get; set; } = string.Empty;\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 密码哈希\n        /// </summary>\n        public string PasswordHash { get; set; } = string.Empty;\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 手机号\n        /// </summary>\n        public string? PhoneNumber { get; set; }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 是否激活\n        /// </summary>\n        public bool IsActive { get; set; } = true;\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 是否已验证邮箱\n        /// </summary>\n        public bool EmailVerified { get; set; } = false;\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 创建时间\n        /// </summary>\n        public DateTime CreatedAt { get; set; } = DateTime.UtcNow;\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 更新时间\n        /// </summary>\n        public DateTime? UpdatedAt { get; set; }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 最后登录时间\n        /// </summary>\n        public DateTime? LastLoginAt { get; set; }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 用户角色列表\n        /// </summary>\n        public ICollection<Role> Roles { get; set; } = new List<Role>();\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 刷新令牌\n        /// </summary>\n        public string? RefreshToken { get; set; }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 刷新令牌过期时间\n        /// </summary>\n        public DateTime? RefreshTokenExpiryTime { get; set; }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227328872}}
{"type":"message","id":"17ddf784","parentId":"b602fb88","timestamp":"2026-03-23T00:55:28.875Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_23e9407007d241199247e6ee","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"using System;\nusing System.Collections.Generic;\nusing System.Linq;\nusing System.Threading.Tasks;\nusing Microsoft.Extensions.Logging;\nusing Tianyou.Auth.Models;\nusing Tianyou.Auth.Security;\n\nnamespace Tianyou.Auth.Services\n{\n    /// <summary>\n    /// 认证服务实现\n    /// </summary>\n    public class AuthService : IAuthService\n    {\n        private readonly TokenService _tokenService;\n        private readonly PasswordHasher _passwordHasher;\n        private readonly ILogger<AuthService> _logger;\n\n        // 模拟用户存储（实际应使用数据库）\n        private static readonly Dictionary<Guid, User> _users = new();\n        private static readonly Dictionary<string, Guid> _usernameIndex = new();\n        private static readonly Dictionary<string, Guid> _emailIndex = new();\n\n        public AuthService(\n            TokenService tokenService,\n            PasswordHasher passwordHasher,\n            ILogger<AuthService> logger)\n        {\n            _tokenService = tokenService;\n            _passwordHasher = passwordHasher;\n            _logger = logger;\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 用户登录\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<LoginResponse> LoginAsync(LoginRequest request)\n        {\n            try\n            {\n                var user = await ValidateUserAsync(request.Username, request.Password);\n                \n                if (user == null)\n                {\n                    return new LoginResponse\n                    {\n                        Success = false,\n                        Message = \"用户名或密码错误\"\n                    };\n                }\n\n                if (!user.IsActive)\n                {\n                    return new LoginResponse\n                    {\n                        Success = false,\n                        Message = \"账户已被禁用\"\n                    };\n                }\n\n                // 获取用户角色和权限\n                var roles = user.Roles.Select(r => r.Name).ToList();\n                var permissions = user.Roles\n                    .SelectMany(r => r.Permissions)\n                    .Select(p => p.Code)\n                    .Distinct()\n                    .ToList();\n\n                // 生成令牌\n                var tokenInfo = _tokenService.CreateTokenInfo(user, roles, permissions);\n\n                // 更新刷新令牌\n                user.RefreshToken = tokenInfo.RefreshToken;\n                user.RefreshTokenExpiryTime = _tokenService.GetRefreshTokenExpiryTime();\n                user.LastLoginAt = DateTime.UtcNow;\n\n                _logger.LogInformation(\"用户 {Username} 登录成功\", user.Username);\n\n                return new LoginResponse\n                {\n                    Success = true,\n                    Message = \"登录成功\",\n                    TokenInfo = tokenInfo\n                };\n            }\n            catch (Exception ex)\n            {\n                _logger.LogError(ex, \"用户登录失败: {Username}\", request.Username);\n                return new LoginResponse\n                {\n                    Success = false,\n                    Message = \"登录失败，请稍后重试\"\n                };\n            }\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 用户登出\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<bool> LogoutAsync(Guid userId)\n        {\n            try\n            {\n                if (_users.TryGetValue(userId, out var user))\n                {\n                    user.RefreshToken = null;\n                    user.RefreshTokenExpiryTime = null;\n                    _logger.LogInformation(\"用户 {Username} 登出成功\", user.Username);\n                }\n                return await Task.FromResult(true);\n            }\n            catch (Exception ex)\n            {\n                _logger.LogError(ex, \"用户登出失败: {UserId}\", userId);\n                return false;\n            }\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 刷新令牌\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<TokenInfo?> RefreshTokenAsync(string refreshToken)\n        {\n            try\n            {\n                var user = _users.Values.FirstOrDefault(u => u.RefreshToken == refreshToken);\n\n                if (user == null || user.RefreshTokenExpiryTime <= DateTime.UtcNow)\n                {\n                    return null;\n                }\n\n                var roles = user.Roles.Select(r => r.Name).ToList();\n                var permissions = user.Roles\n                    .SelectMany(r => r.Permissions)\n                    .Select(p => p.Code)\n                    .Distinct()\n                    .ToList();\n\n                var tokenInfo = _tokenService.CreateTokenInfo(user, roles, permissions);\n\n                user.RefreshToken = tokenInfo.RefreshToken;\n                user.RefreshTokenExpiryTime = _tokenService.GetRefreshTokenExpiryTime();\n\n                _logger.LogInformation(\"用户 {Username} 刷新令牌成功\", user.Username);\n\n                return await Task.FromResult(tokenInfo);\n            }\n            catch (Exception ex)\n            {\n                _logger.LogError(ex, \"刷新令牌失败\");\n                return null;\n            }\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 验证用户\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<User?> ValidateUserAsync(string username, string password)\n        {\n            if (!_usernameIndex.TryGetValue(username.ToLower(), out var userId))\n            {\n                return null;\n            }\n\n            if (!_users.TryGetValue(userId, out var user))\n            {\n                return null;\n            }\n\n            if (!_passwordHasher.VerifyPassword(password, user.PasswordHash))\n            {\n                return null;\n            }\n\n            return await Task.FromResult(user);\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 注册新用户\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<User> RegisterAsync(string username, string email, string password, string? phoneNumber = null)\n        {\n            if (await UserExistsAsync(username, email))\n            {\n                throw new InvalidOperationException(\"用户名或邮箱已存在\");\n            }\n\n            var user = new User\n            {\n                Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n                Username = username,\n                Email = email,\n                PasswordHash = _passwordHasher.HashPassword(password),\n                PhoneNumber = phoneNumber,\n                IsActive = true,\n                EmailVerified = false,\n                CreatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow\n            };\n\n            // 分配默认角色\n            var defaultRole = new Role\n            {\n                Id = Guid.NewGuid(),\n                Name = \"User\",\n                Code = \"user\",\n                Description = \"普通用户\",\n                IsSystem = true\n            };\n            user.Roles.Add(defaultRole);\n\n            _users[user.Id] = user;\n            _usernameIndex[username.ToLower()] = user.Id;\n            _emailIndex[email.ToLower()] = user.Id;\n\n            _logger.LogInformation(\"新用户注册成功: {Username}\", username);\n\n            return await Task.FromResult(user);\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 修改密码\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<bool> ChangePasswordAsync(Guid userId, string oldPassword, string newPassword)\n        {\n            if (!_users.TryGetValue(userId, out var user))\n            {\n                return false;\n            }\n\n            if (!_passwordHasher.VerifyPassword(oldPassword, user.PasswordHash))\n            {\n                return false;\n            }\n\n            user.PasswordHash = _passwordHasher.HashPassword(newPassword);\n            user.UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow;\n            user.RefreshToken = null;\n            user.RefreshTokenExpiryTime = null;\n\n            _logger.LogInformation(\"用户 {Username} 修改密码成功\", user.Username);\n\n            return await Task.FromResult(true);\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 重置密码\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<bool> ResetPasswordAsync(string email)\n        {\n            if (!_emailIndex.TryGetValue(email.ToLower(), out var userId))\n            {\n                return false;\n            }\n\n            // 实际实现应发送邮件\n            _logger.LogInformation(\"密码重置请求: {Email}\", email);\n            return await Task.FromResult(true);\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 验证邮箱\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<bool> VerifyEmailAsync(Guid userId, string verificationCode)\n        {\n            if (!_users.TryGetValue(userId, out var user))\n            {\n                return false;\n            }\n\n            // 实际实现应验证验证码\n            user.EmailVerified = true;\n            user.UpdatedAt = DateTime.UtcNow;\n\n            _logger.LogInformation(\"用户 {Username} 邮箱验证成功\", user.Username);\n\n            return await Task.FromResult(true);\n        }\n\n        /// <summary>\n        /// 检查用户是否存在\n        /// </summary>\n        public async Task<bool> UserExistsAsync(string username, string email)\n        {\n            var exists = _usernameIndex.ContainsKey(username.ToLower()) ||\n                        _emailIndex.ContainsKey(email.ToLower());\n            return await Task.FromResult(exists);\n        }\n    }\n}\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774227328875}}
